Please edit this element's data and check to ensure the id is correct.        Maps, brochures, and publications of Obed Wild and Scenic River can be obtained at the visitor center, located at 208 North Maiden Street in downtown Wartburg, Tennessee. If you cannot make it to the visitor center, but still would like a map/brochure, please download the park map [494 kb PDF], or write to:  Obed WSR PO Box 429 Wartburg, TN 37887 You may also obtain a map/brochure by calling us at (423) 346-6294.     Obed Vicinity Map
